{"tid":989720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真筍盤】西西里島山城賤價賣屋 畀$8.9就可做業主","createTime":"2019-01-21T05:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T07:17:14.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"54ae9636585cb44cdc7006dabcdde015a498076c","tid":989720,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547981728_8cc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547981728_8cc5.jpg&h=d3be5168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547981729_42bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547981729_42bc.jpg&h=d6d6195e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你有否想過移居到意大利呢？如果有，現在便有大好機會，西西里島山城珊布卡（Sambuca）有數十間房屋待價而沽，而且售價只是1歐元（8.9港元）而已。珊布卡副鎮長卡喬波（Giuseppe Cacioppo）強調，此舉並非宣傳，旨在鼓勵人們搬到當地居住，藉此振興經濟及令人口增長。<br />\n<br />\n去年2月，撒丁島的奧洛萊鎮（Ollolai）也推出類似活動，200多間房屋售價不到1.1歐元（9.7港元）。卡喬波強調售屋並非宣傳，市政府擁有所有出售房屋的業權，「我們並非是屋主與買家之間的中間人，只要你想買屋，就可以立刻入住。」<br />\n<br />\n出售的房屋面積介乎40至150平方米，但全部都要進行大規模維修，有意買屋者必須在3年內至少花1.65萬歐元（14.6萬港元）維修。新業主同時亦要支付5,500歐元（4.8萬港元）保證金，當裝修完成後便會退還。<br />\n<br />\n卡喬波稱反應十分熱烈，獲得不少來自法國、瑞士及西班牙的人士接洽，現時已經賣出10間，但仍有數十個單位供選擇。<br />\n<br />\n他又自誇珊布卡位於一個歷史悠久的自然保護區內，四周被海灘、森林和山脈環繞，鎮內寧靜祥和，實在是人間天堂。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59163781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59163781&d=mfnejbsFhuLinHjNFaGmHG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e130a026\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59163781&h=417ecf6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59163781</a>"},{"pid":"39a8a1334f5a284c0877c68b8ec67184d679590b","tid":989720,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"一個香港單位掃晒全個島"},{"pid":"528aab0a57c796bdc8308b16d029496aa1820b3f","tid":989720,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"Godfather feel"},{"pid":"d722ce072445104f63724b094ece97b4ce9ef356","tid":989720,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a8a1334f5a284c0877c68b8ec67184d679590b","tid":989720,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"一個香港單位掃晒全個島"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"城個島買曬自住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b4b25f3736339da36550432392f327478567b6","tid":989720,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"michael corleone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d91aa121888a116ba68e220ed97c94ed99dd238","tid":989720,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a8a1334f5a284c0877c68b8ec67184d679590b","tid":989720,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"一個香港單位掃晒全個島"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"係個車位已經搞掂哂<br />\n可能包埋裝俢"},{"pid":"4e71c33d664abe40da67795ccee8ad2ef7098f8c","tid":989720,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"要俾十幾皮裝修"},{"pid":"7f7df22940ab4c87411d75154b508aef496c1fab","tid":989720,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e71c33d664abe40da67795ccee8ad2ef7098f8c","tid":989720,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"要俾十幾皮裝修"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"十幾皮咁平. 買黎開airbnb, 渡假都抵."},{"